text: “khran meux brrda deuxn txng ham hela nan di phan phn pi læw k cng prahatprahar mu chrik hela nan n thi dı ktam thi phwk cea phb phwk khea læa cng cab phwk khea læa cng lxm phwk khea læa cng nang sxdsxng phwk khea thuk cud thi sxng sxng tæ tha phwk khea sa hnuk phi kk lab taw læa darng wi sung kar lahmad læa chara sa kat læw sir k cng plxy phwk khea pi thæ cring xallxh nan pen phu thrx phay thosʹ phuthrng xendu metta”
